response.overview: On December 09, 2017, at Texport Imabari in Imabari, Ehime, Japan, NJPW World Tag League 2017 - Day 18 took place. The event was broadcast on NJPWWorld.com.  The card featured a mix of tag team and ten-man matches, including a Six Man Tag Team match between Los Ingobernables de Japon and CHAOS. Other notable matches included Hirooki Goto and YOSHI-HASHI vs Suzuki-gun's El Desperado and Minoru Suzuki, and TenKoji's Hiroyoshi Tenzan and Satoshi Kojima versus BULLET CLUB's Bad Luck Fale, Chase Owens, Hangman Page, and Yujiro Takahashi.  Other wrestlers on the show include Hiroshi Tanahashi, Kenny Omega, and Will Ospreay.
response.title: NJPW World Tag League 2017 - Day 18
